You can simply ask Alexa to control your MeshHub supported products. After connecting Alexa to your products in a few simple steps:
(1) Download our MeshHub app in app market then register an account;
(2) Configure our devices in MeshHub app and change appropriate name for your devices;
(3) Enable MeshHub skill, and you'll be navigated to MeshHub login page;
(4) Follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
(5) Now all setup is finished. You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
Alexa, turn on plug.
Alexa, turn off plug.
Alexa, turn on the bedroom light.
Alexa, turn off the bedroom light.
Alexa, set the bedroom light to 50%.
Alexa, set bedroom light to green.
